name: GHOST IN THE SHELL S.A.C. X MetaSamurai

metadata.name: GHOST IN THE SHELL S.A.C. X MetaSamurai #1
metadata.description: Inspired by the soul and energy born from the counter-culture movement; a shared interest between 1BLOCK STUDIO and Ghost In The Shell, the design reflects the chaotic nature of TOKYO as a melting pot of various subcultures and questioning the essence of counter-culture in this fast-spaced world.
